{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"39107058cc","title":"关于改进《人民日报》工作的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"353cad4483","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":13,"articleId":"39107058cc"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"66545c9d21","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"39107058cc","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"乔木，即胡乔木，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、毛泽东的秘书。"},{"id":"3ad8fc0597","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"39107058cc","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是《人民日报》一篇社论（清样稿）的题目。毛泽东审阅时，将题目改为《正确地对待善意的批评》。这篇社论发表在1957年6月13日《人民日报》上。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a374e180ac","type":"title","text":"关于改进《人民日报》工作的批语\"","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"39107058cc"},{"id":"66545c9d21","type":"paragraph","text":"养木同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"39107058cc"},{"id":"3ad8fc0597","type":"paragraph","text":"北京日报比人民日内（报）编得好，有工人、农民、学生、左翼党外人士的批判反动言论的大量报道，极为手富，文字也较人民日报生动，编排也好。请看第二版全部报道","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"39107058cc"},{"id":"b117a628d3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"39107058cc"},{"id":"7adfee8fa3","type":"paragraph","text":"六月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"39107058cc"},{"id":"a2891c957f","type":"paragraph","text":"请在人【民了日报召集一个会议，有较多人参加。事先要他们读这第二版，全部读一遍，然后开会。你的编排水平应当提高。文","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"39107058cc"},{"id":"d3654e9426","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这两条批语写在1957年6月12日《北京日报》第一版上。字也有些八股味，例如不感觉“怎样对待「对待】批评”三这个概念化的标题是不好的，不感觉这篇文章通体是一个八股调。希望思索改进。","